data.description: Check out this remodeled 3 bed 2 bath corner lot home! Renovated Cabinets, full interior and exterior paint, new carpet, and lots of added lighting! This move-in ready home also features soaring vaulted ceilings, RV access and pre-wired electrical for RV hook-up, a covered patio, and a fully Landscaped Backyard! Don't wait to schedule your appointments!   Sellers are offering $5000.00 towards buyer's closing costs or rate buy down.
